[section#range.split.overview
    [:en] Overview
    [:zh_CN] 概述
]

[para]
[:en] [`split_view] takes a [`:c view] and a delimiter, and splits the [`:c view]
into subranges on the delimiter.
[:zh_CN] [`split_view] 接受一个 [`:c view] 和一个分隔符，并将该 [`:c view] 根据
这个分隔符分成子范围。

[:en] The delimiter can be a single element or a [`:c view] of elements.
[:zh_CN] 分隔符可以是单个元素或者一个元素的 [`:c view]。

[para]
[begin:example]
[codeblock]
string str{"the quick brown fox"};
split_view sentence{str, ' '};
for (auto word : sentence) {
  for (char ch : word)
    cout << ch;
  cout << '*';
}
// [:en] The above prints: the*quick*brown*fox* \
   [:zh_CN] 以上代码打印出：the*quick*brown*fox*
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]
